title: Voting gets underway in Italy's election
text:
Voting gets underway in Italy's election Saturday, March 03, 2018 - 01:46 
Italians go to the polls on Sunday (March 4) in a vote that could bring political gridlock after an election campaign marked by anger over the listless economy, high unemployment and immigration. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
